<section id="content" role="main" class="group calculator-page">

  <header class="page-header group">
    <hgroup class="full-width">
      <h1><span>Quick answer</span> Child Benefit tax calculator</h1>
    <div class="article-container-start group">
  <article role="article" class="group"><div class="inner">
      <div class="intro">
          <p>Use this tool to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>work out how much Child Benefit you receive in a tax year</li>
            <li>estimate how much Child Benefit to pay back as a tax charge</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="get-started">
            <a rel="nofollow" href="/child-benefit-tax-calculator/process_form" class="big button">Start now</a>
          </div>
            <div id="before-you-start">
              <h2>Before you start</h2>
              <p>You’ll need:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>the dates Child Benefit started and, if applicable, stopped</li>
                <li>your basic income details</li>
              </ul>
              <p>You may have to pay some or all of your Child Benefit back as a tax charge if you or your partner’s individual adjusted net income is over £50,000.</p>
             </div> 
      </div>
</div>
